{
  "id": "adv_event_2303_01_04",
  "title": "すみれの魅力",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――合宿開始から数時間後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few hours later after camp started",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 2.7800000668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "……新ユニット、なかなか……決まらない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…The new unit‚ it's quite… difficult to decide…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.9666666667,
      "endTime": 7.7280271213,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "買ってきたお菓子もストック切れです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The snacks we bought are running out too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.9213603974,
      "endTime": 11.622267437,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "ほとんどあなたが食べてませんでした！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You almost ate all of them!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.8289340179,
      "endTime": 14.6743768375,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "えー、すずにゃんだっていっぱい食べてましたよ～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh‚ Suzu-nyan‚ you ate a lot too‚ you know~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.8810434183,
      "endTime": 19.3383224329,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "もう……二人ともだよ～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Honestly… you two…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.5449889661,
      "endTime": 22.2642632962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "（……もう随分長い時間、会議してるな）\n（みんな疲れてきてるし、私がしっかりしないと……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（We've been in this meeting for quite a while now.）\n（Everyone seems tired‚ I need to be firm…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.4783222994,
      "endTime": 31.661995967299998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあみんな！　これまで出たアイデアを\n一回、整理してみようよ。何か思いつくかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ everyone! Let's organize the ideas\nwe've come up with so far. Maybe something new will come up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.8783222994,
      "endTime": 38.8974151453,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、そうは言いましても……\nみんな、ネタも体力も尽きているのでは？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh‚ even if you say that…\nAren't we running out of ideas and energy?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.1116556328,
      "endTime": 47.3159639519,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも……今日中に決めないと、さとみさんが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… if we don't decide by today‚ Satomi-san will…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.5226303896,
      "endTime": 52.5451021036,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04-stm001.m4a",
      "text": "…………あれー？　もしかして私、勘違いしてたかも？\nいやいや、してました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh? Wait a minute? Did I maybe misunderstand something?\nNo no‚ I definitely did!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.755963723,
      "endTime": 60.5479816597,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04-stm002.m4a",
      "text": "新ユニットの企画の締切、明日じゃありませんでした！\n来週でした！　すみません、私ったらうっかり者で！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The deadline for the new unit's proposal wasn't tomorrow!\nIt's next week! I'm so sorry‚ I'm such a scatterbrain!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.741315794,
      "endTime": 69.3638334911,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ええー！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.5583451431,
      "endTime": 71.0305018108,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04-stm003.m4a",
      "text": "ほんっとーに、ごめんなさい！\nですから、会議はひと休みしましょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm really‚ really sorry!\nSo‚ should we take a break from the meeting?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.4964748024,
      "endTime": 76.8929780601,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "まったくもう！　さとみさんは人騒がせですわね！\nでも私は寛大ですから、もちろん許して差し上げます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Honestly! Satomi-san is such a troublemaker!\nBut I'm generous‚ so of course‚ I'll forgive her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.0796447078,
      "endTime": 85.9352229396,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "（……もしかしてさとみさん、空気が悪いのを察して）\n（嘘、ついてくれたのかな……？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Could it be that Satomi-san sensed the tension in the air?）\n（So‚ she lied purposely…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.1218896825,
      "endTime": 93.7641347844,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04-stm004.m4a",
      "text": "夕食は、私がカレーを作りますから休んでいて下さい\n……あれー？　どうしたんです、奥山さん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll make curry for dinner‚ so rest up.\n…Huh? What's wrong‚ Okuyama-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.9552230159,
      "endTime": 103.3581152601,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "……さとみさん、私も手伝います！\nじゃがいも剥きなら、目を閉じてたって出来ますよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Satomi-san‚ I'll help too!\nI can peel potatoes even with my eyes closed!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.564893337,
      "endTime": 111.8963445623,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "カレーですか？\nこころは本格派インドカリーを希望します～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Curry‚ huh?\nI want authentic Indian curry~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.0982266704,
      "endTime": 116.7665938655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "私はインドより欧風がいいですわ！\nそもそもカレーの起源は――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I prefer European-style over Indian!\nBut then again‚ the origin of curry is.――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.9532605607,
      "endTime": 121.945754667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "え、ええーっ！？\n私、ハチミツ入りの甘口がいいよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh‚ ehh!?\nI like mild curry with honey~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.052419865,
      "endTime": 127.1616034626,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "すみれちゃん、お子様口ですね～。可愛いですね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire-chan‚ you have such a childlike taste~ So cute~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.352419865,
      "endTime": 132.4643471836,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "むー！　そんなことないもん！　お兄ちゃんだって\n私のカレー美味しいって言ってくれてるもん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mm! That's not true!\nEven my big brother says my curry is great!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.6776804883,
      "endTime": 139.2933042486,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04-stm005.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、ちょっとみなさ～ん？\nケンカはダメですよ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "H-Hey everyone?\nFighting is not allowed~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.4776804883,
      "endTime": 143.6505862194,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "カレーには……みんな、それぞれこだわりがある……\n一見、鉄板だけど……実は、危険なメニュー……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone has… their own… preferences when it comes to curry…\nIt seems like a solid choice‚ but… it's actually a risky menu…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.8572527526,
      "endTime": 152.2592253327,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あはは……。でもなんだか\n林間学校で行ったキャンプを思い出すな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ ahaha… But somehow\nit reminds me of the camp we did during school.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.4525586087,
      "endTime": 160.0628308254,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "あの時も、こうやってみんなでお泊りして\nカレーを作ったけど……楽しかったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Back then‚ we all stayed overnight and\nmade curry together… It was fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.2525586087,
      "endTime": 167.9406310994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "林間学校？　……そういう学校の行事って\n私、いつも仕事で行けなかったな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "School camp?\n…I always missed those because of work…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.1525586087,
      "endTime": 176.94432744570003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "……ふふっ。でもそっか、こういう感じなんだね\n凄く、楽しいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hehe. But I see‚ it's something like this.\nIt's really‚ really fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.1525586087,
      "endTime": 186.2165900189,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
