      "text": "温かいお茶です。缶入りですけど\n……落ち着きました？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Here's some warm tea. It's canned though.\n…Are you feeling calmer now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 391.2385790468,
      "endTime": 397.8137817979,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "……ごめんなさい。私まで一緒になって騒いじゃって\nさとみさん。締切が来週って……嘘ですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I'm sorry. I got carried away and made a racket too.\nSatomi-san. It's a lie that deadline is next week… right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 398.0137817979,
      "endTime": 410.7950516343,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04-stm010.m4a",
      "text": "……あはは、気付かれちゃってましたか、ごめんなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ahaha‚ you noticed‚ huh? Sorry about that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 410.9804484646,
      "endTime": 417.4601350109,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04-smr017.m4a",
      "text": "なのに、さとみさんの手伝いも\nまとめ役も全然出来なくて……私、ダメだなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And yet‚ even with Satomi-san's help…\nI couldn't even organize things properly… I'm no good…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 417.6601350109,
      "endTime": 428.22222092550004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04-stm011.m4a",
      "text": "いいんです。奥山さん、とっても楽しそうでしたから\n凄くいい表情をしてましたよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's okay. Okuyama-san. You seemed like you were having a lot of fun.\nYou made a really nice face‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 428.4268016775,
      "endTime": 435.3755024277,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04-stm012.m4a",
      "text": "奥山さん、修学旅行とか林間学校とかは\nお仕事で行ったことないんでしたよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okuyama-san‚ you've never been on a school trip\nor a camp for work‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 435.6424768726,
      "endTime": 442.1245795527,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_04-smr018.m4a",
      "text": "はい、きっとこんな風なんだろうな、楽しいなって\nついはしゃいじゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ that's probably how it feels‚ huh? It's so much fun…\nthat I got carried away…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 442.3179129242,
      "endTime": 449.984579718,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
